diaMCP is an all-in-one Model Context Protocol (MCP) server designed
for integration with llama.cpp webui.

It provides many built-in tools including:
- File operations (read, write, list, etc.)
- Web search and fetch (via DDGS)
- Git operations (clone, pull)
- Shell command execution
- Python code evaluation
- yfinance stock data
- Custom tool support

This port installs diaMCP as a native Python application and provides
an rc.d script for easy service management.

WWW: https://github.com/chartrambiz/diaMCP
